{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"5d11accea20a90e0a4ecabc681088233350857002c8757d9500994645fba3804","slug":"seismology.seismograph","location":"/seismology/seismograph.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"地震仪","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101","numbering":{"title":{"offset":1}},"source_url":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101/blob/main/source/seismology/seismograph.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101/edit/main/source/seismology/seismograph.md","thumbnail":"/seismology101/build/seismograph-dbefe6c537dfeb98ec05563d0cca2bab.jpg","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"seismograph.md","url":"/seismology101/build/seismograph-c3debe94139d3ae9082efefcb25ce585.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"本节贡献者: {{姚家园}}、{{田冬冬}}","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"yynHpsprLO"}],"key":"ETKEov7Vxw"}],"key":"DnwKctfLA3"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近更新日期: 2023-04-19","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"key":"xU7dXVJHoq"}],"key":"KyUj7LooXL"}],"key":"xDKDNgiIZU"}],"key":"ed4zqquDpq"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基本原理","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"key":"MlCJ63xku9"}],"identifier":"id","label":"基本原理","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"WYdkKdDuxs"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震仪（seismograph）是检测和记录地面质点运动（位移、速度、加速度、转动等）的仪器，\n主要由地震计（seismometer）和数据记录系统组成。其中，地震计用于直接拾取地面运动并将其转换\n为符合数据记录系统需要的能量形式，而数据记录系统用于记录地面运动。","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"oWj5r1n6Hu"}],"key":"fLpbCTqoDN"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如以下卡通图所示，固定在地表的框架上挂有弹簧，并将重物悬挂在弹簧上，可以形象表示地震计；\n固定在框架上的旋转的鼓形象地代表了数据记录系统。当地球表面振动时，框架、弹簧、鼓随之移动，\n而重物悬浮不动。若在重物上固定一支笔，则地表和重物之间的相对运动就会被笔在旋转的鼓面上描绘出来，\n鼓面记录到的运动轨迹代表了地面质点运动，即地震图（seismogram）。可以看出，地震仪的基本原理\n是惯性定律。","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"U0pTTJUqhh"}],"key":"cjarPDjG0t"},{"type":"container","kind":"figure","children":[{"type":"image","url":"/seismology101/build/seismograph-dbefe6c537dfeb98ec05563d0cca2bab.jpg","alt":"地震仪的原理示意图","width":"50%","align":"center","urlSource":"seismograph.jpg","key":"pBoIPfPuBV"},{"type":"caption","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震仪的原理示意图。引自\n","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"aUZIqkZsR7"},{"type":"link","url":"https://www.iris.edu/hq/inclass/fact-sheet/how_does_a_seismometer_work","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How Does a Seismometer Work?","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"FxHeFZw8Qv"}],"urlSource":"https://www.iris.edu/hq/inclass/fact-sheet/how_does_a_seismometer_work","key":"EFYmwzFCDd"}],"key":"atfTRZTRA1"}],"key":"b3hZ3vH3r7"}],"enumerator":"1","key":"qx84dD8kLN"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震学研究中使用的地震仪对地面运动高度敏感，在非常安静的地区，甚至可以检测到 1 纳米的位移，\n几乎与原子间距一样小。大地震（如 2004 年印度尼西亚的苏门答腊地震）产生的地震波可以被全球范围\n的地震仪记录到，振幅高达到几厘米。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"ItJFA4jdwV"}],"key":"F5V1H5Ww6C"}],"key":"gqdwmoQpf2"}],"key":"MP49BC8nQ7"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}},"footer":{"navigation":{"prev":{"title":"地震图","url":"/seismology/seismogram","group":"地震学基础"},"next":{"title":"地震台站","url":"/seismology/station","group":"地震学基础"}}},"domain":"http://localhost:3000"}